The '''Echani vibrosword''' was a type of long [[Vibroblade/Legends|vibroblade]] that was manufactured by the [[Echani/Legends|Echani]]. Made with a [[Cortosis/Legends|cortosis]] weave, the blade of this melee weapon was resistant to [[Lightsaber/Legends|lightsaber]] strikes, which enabled them to be used against [[Force-sensitive/Legends|Force-users]]. In addition to this, they were sometimes supercooled during production in order to maintain alignment. This had the added effect of giving an icy sting to those struck by this weapon.

